{"id": "1244285179216920717", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 19, "author_id": "372020544494764043", "author_name": "ariate", "author_bot": false, "content": "在等環拉時可以試一下拉加聚首或洞悉", "timestamp": "2024-05-26T13:45:04.426000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1241851407414333475"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1243928627364495472", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1244285668725624932", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 0, "author_id": "372020544494764043", "author_name": "ariate", "author_bot": false, "content": "前者是複製己方好用麻痹，等拉狂氣爆發時直接連技，後者控對面牌序順便抄一張。", "timestamp": "2024-05-26T13:47:01.134000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1244286383816835083", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 0, "author_id": "372020544494764043", "author_name": "ariate", "author_bot": false, "content": "然後回血可以試一下羊媽，可以幫圖姆引一下火力，隨了沒得復活外，他的單補40（自己20）和充狂氣也太強了，對面不先解決就補到對面崩潰。所以圖姆可更易活下來", "timestamp": "2024-05-26T13:49:51.625000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1244286610820825230", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 0, "author_id": "372020544494764043", "author_name": "ariate", "author_bot": false, "content": "如果是聚首軸的話，羊媽的4費預備也可以複制下來，歐起來天胡也很誇張", "timestamp": "2024-05-26T13:50:45.747000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1244292326294028302", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 19, "author_id": "1241851407414333475", "author_name": "lyaistra", "author_bot": false, "content": "好的感谢 之前带的羊妈和拉辅助手感还行 我换换命轮再试试", "timestamp": "2024-05-26T14:13:28.422000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["372020544494764043"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1244285179216920717", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1244293096951382046", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 0, "author_id": "451726402488631306", "author_name": "rainbowteemo", "author_bot": false, "content": "環拉感覺真的很強", "timestamp": "2024-05-26T14:16:32.161000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1244294080276463626", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 0, "author_id": "451726402488631306", "author_name": "rainbowteemo", "author_bot": false, "content": "3費和4費的含金量完全不同", "timestamp": "2024-05-26T14:20:26.604000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1244294079626350673", "filename": "Screenshot_20240526_221739.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 448281, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1180850818509971466/1244294079626350673/Screenshot_20240526_221739.jpg?ex=6a374a6a&is=6a35f8ea&hm=c0c1524fd129e16e06036d2ff1cc0eded7e259572ebf699653c305adce342148&"}, {"id": "1244294080033329172", "filename": "Screenshot_20240526_221725.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 463242, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1180850818509971466/1244294080033329172/Screenshot_20240526_221725.jpg?ex=6a374a6a&is=6a35f8ea&hm=4da47fe2240c17e18511b2c09300272e7956dbbfe066220877129bff042f8299&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1244295525260333088", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 0, "author_id": "451726402488631306", "author_name": "rainbowteemo", "author_bot": false, "content": "(控90氣和80氣的難度也根本不是同個等級", "timestamp": "2024-05-26T14:26:11.115000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1244348025879658557", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 19, "author_id": "372020544494764043", "author_name": "ariate", "author_bot": false, "content": "", "timestamp": "2024-05-26T17:54:48.238000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1241851407414333475"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1244348025674141746", "filename": "image0.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 162248, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1180850818509971466/1244348025674141746/image0.jpg?ex=6a377ca8&is=6a362b28&hm=d72f00e08ac21bd52b856db398857243181dafea8efaab782dcc26dd31ac6dde&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1244292326294028302", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1244348422258036768", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 0, "author_id": "372020544494764043", "author_name": "ariate", "author_bot": false, "content": "幫你試了一下，由1600掉到1400再上回來。\n勝率在1500左右分域應該算過半，你可以試一下。", "timestamp": "2024-05-26T17:56:22.742000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1244350407879430227", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 0, "author_id": "372020544494764043", "author_name": "ariate", "author_bot": false, "content": "雖然玩著玩著就把圖姆和艾瑞卡換珊和莉茲了，聚首配莉茲的強度太直觀了，然後珊是為了上虛弱，除了嘲諷外，多一個控，而且她的30自充令這個控更易出現。此外，她的牌也算是被複製了都很不錯的進攻牌，2費疊攻複製多了後，殘局很強。", "timestamp": "2024-05-26T18:04:16.151000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
